Summer EBT Outreach Toolkit" https://hungerfreenj.org/summer-ebt-2024/
Get started! Fill out an intake form and one of our Resource Specialists will get back to you.
Steps to fill out form:

Click "Get Started" (select I am not a robot)
Select Spanish or English
Enter the information requested 
Make sure to include the most up-to-date contact information
Fill out as much information as possible 
Submit the profile 
A Resource Specialist will contact you for further information
